9. brill-lindquist-9-res256.par

Same *irreducible* mass ratio as BL-3 and same *proper* distance as BL-6

par_b = 0.40480421586           # half separation
par_m_minus = 0.814259649085    # mass of m+ puncture
par_m_plus = 0.485740350915     # mass of m- puncture

R_max = 10.0        # outer boundary
T_max = 5.0         # simulation end time
T_fine = 4.0        # begin of fine output



