14. brill-lindquist-14-res256.par

Between BL-2 and BL-3, i.e. coordinate distance d=1.1

par_b = 0.55        # half separation
par_m_minus = 0.8   # mass of m+ puncture
par_m_plus = 0.5    # mass of m- puncture

R_max = 10.0        # outer boundary
